Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Michael — a founder who's built\Nand scaled companies across the United\NStates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I want to show you one platform that\Ncompletely changed how I run marketing and\Noperations: Pzhisen — that's pzhisen.online.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting started is incredibly simple,\Nfast, and convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You open the site, share your business idea, and\Ndeploy your AI employee team in minutes — no\Ncomplicated setup, no credit card required to\Nbegin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once your agents are live, they work for you\Ntwenty-four hours a day, seven days a week,\Nthree hundred sixty-five days a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They never sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They never take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They never clock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With Pzhisen, specialized AI agents\Nautomatically create promotional marketing\Ntweets and social copy for your brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They produce promotional marketing\Nvideos ready for distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They write promotional marketing emails\Nand send them to mainstream inboxes\Nworldwide — Gmail, Outlook, and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically reply to customer\Nservice messages, so your clients always\Nget help — day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically analyze your market\Ncompetitiveness, your sales data, and\Nreal-time market conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They research industry trends and help\Nyou understand where the world's major\Nsectors are heading next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they publish for you across the world's\Nbiggest platforms: YouTube, TikTok, X, Facebook,\NWeChat Channels, Douyin, Tencent Video,\NKuaishou, Xiaohongshu — and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you have a personal website or a full\Nenterprise site, Pzhisen helps anyone, anywhere,\Npromote and grow online — fully automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the result that matters most: Pzhisen has\Nalready helped thousands of individuals and businesses\Nworldwide generate one million dollars in revenue in a\Nsingle month through AI-powered promotion and marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ready to put an AI team to\Nwork while you sleep, go to\Npzhisen.online — and start tonight.
